text: Fantasea is a word play on fantasy and sea. It may refer to: ==Shipping== *Fantasea Cruising, operating ferries and water taxis on Sydney Harbour and Pittwater - Taken over by NRMA in 2018. *Fantaseas, a defunct chain of indoor waterparks in the United Kingdom *Fantasea, a 1978 surf movie with Shaun Tomson ==Music== *Fantasea (mixtape), a mixtape by Azealia Banks
title: Fantasea
